===Verb===
'''to colorize'''

# to add color to
#: ''The child '''colorized''' the drawing.''
#: ''The woman '''colorized''' her hair.''
# to convert a [[black and white]] [[film]] or [[photography]] to [[color]] using a [[computer]] assisted process
#: There is a '''colorized''' version of Casablanca.''

